# Build output
/zerostrike
/zerostrike.exe
dist/

# Go
*.test
*.out
coverage.html

# Project state
# .zerostrike/ is created under whatever directory is scanned (the repo
# root when running `zerostrike scan .`, but also e.g. benchmark/corpus/*
# when the benchmark tool scans each corpus case as its own root) - a
# pattern with a slash in the middle is anchored to this file's directory
# in gitignore syntax, so it must be **/-prefixed to match at any depth.
**/.zerostrike/

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# docs/ is intentionally tracked (release notes, architecture docs)